## 7. SELF-LEARNING SYSTEM

This is the moat. No per-client VPS model can do this.

### How it works

All client data lives in one Supabase project (with tenant isolation via `tenant_id` + RLS). This means:

**Pattern detection across all clients:**
- "Clients who set 5+ goals in week 1 have 60% lower execution scores than those who set 3"
- "Wednesday is the lowest execution day across 78% of clients"
- "Clients who respond to the 17:00 check-in within 30 minutes have 2.3× higher weekly scores"

**Feedback loop into the system prompt:**
- Monthly: aggregate anonymized patterns from all clients
- Update the Claude system prompt with proven nudges
- A/B test different accountability styles (confrontational vs. supportive)
- Track which morning briefing formats lead to higher execution

**For the client:** "This system has helped 47 professionals improve their execution score by an average of 34 points." That's social proof you can only build with multi-tenant data.

**For you:** Every client makes every other client's experience better. That's a compounding advantage no coach or per-client VPS can match.

### Data isolation

- Every table has `tenant_id` column
- Supabase Row Level Security (RLS) ensures clients only see their own data
- Aggregate analytics are anonymized (no PII in cross-client patterns)
- Client can request full data export at any time (GDPR compliance)
- Client can request deletion at any time

