## 10. TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE

### 10.1 Overview — one system, all clients

```
                    MULTI-TENANT (your Proxmox)
                    ─────────────────────────────
                    ├── n8n (webhook handler + cron triggers)
                    ├── Ollama (IE scoring, shared)
                    ├── Postiz (social publishing, Phase 2)
